.SH NAME
drm_client_register \- Register client
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_client_register
.BI "(struct drm_client_dev *client "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "client" 12
DRM client
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Add the client to the \fIdrm_device\fP client list to activate its callbacks.
\fIclient\fP must be initialized by a call to \fBdrm_client_init\fP. After
\fBdrm_client_register\fP it is no longer permissible to call \fBdrm_client_release\fP
directly (outside the unregister callback), instead cleanup will happen
automatically on driver unload.
